********>Bugfix 2:
Author:  Scott Brozell
Date:  Feb 17, 2011

Program:  dock

Description:  test orientrigidcontactprimaryzou_gbsasecondarymulti was
incorrectly named  orientflexiblecontactprimaryzou_gbsasecondarymulti
in the zou_gbsa_score Makefile.  This caused make test to complain and
had side effects including stale reference outputs:
make[1]: *** No rule to make target `orientflexiblecontactprimaryzou_gbsasecondarymulti.dockout'.  Stop.

Fix:  make the following changes, most simply accomplished with the command
cd $DOCK_HOME; patch -N -p0 < bugfix.2
to the files:
install/test/zou_gbsa_score/Makefile
install/test/zou_gbsa_score/README
install/test/zou_gbsa_score/orientrigidcontactprimaryzou_gbsasecondarymulti.dockout.save
install/test/zou_gbsa_score/orientrigidcontactprimaryzou_gbsasecondarymulti_primary_scored.mol2.save
-------------------------------------------------------------------------
*** install/test/zou_gbsa_score/Makefile	12 Jul 2009 11:51:33 -0000	1.8
--- install/test/zou_gbsa_score/Makefile	17 Feb 2011 21:25:49 -0000
***************
*** 5,11 ****
  docking:
  	-make zou_gbsaprimary.dockout verbosezou_gbsaprimary \
  	      orientflexiblezou_gbsaprimary.dockout \
! 	      orientflexiblecontactprimaryzou_gbsasecondarymulti.dockout
  
  verbosezou_gbsaprimary:
  	@echo
--- 5,11 ----
  docking:
  	-make zou_gbsaprimary.dockout verbosezou_gbsaprimary \
  	      orientflexiblezou_gbsaprimary.dockout \
! 	      orientrigidcontactprimaryzou_gbsasecondarymulti.dockout
  
  verbosezou_gbsaprimary:
  	@echo
===================================================================
